  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >95 Artworks: Lots of amazing images to bring to life. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start Anywhere: Jump into any level you want. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom Colors: Pick and use your favorite shades.. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chill Music: Relax with a soothing soundtrack. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zoom In: Get up close and perfect every little detail.</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paint by Pixel is such a fun and relaxing game, perfect for getting creative. Imagine a cozy artistic experience where you can color beautiful pixel art, one pixel at a time. Whether you prefer using brush mode for that detailed touch or fill mode to quickly bring your vision to life, it's super easy to personalize your creations just the way you like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/c8c290b2525b8978cf738fc07eee9c5b.poster.avif?t=1729573730\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/c8c290b2525b8978cf738fc07eee9c5b.webm?t=1729573730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/c8c290b2525b8978cf738fc07eee9c5b.mp4?t=1729573730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore unique levels and make sure every pixel is just right. Choose your favorite colors and make each artwork truly your own. Controls are simple and beginner-friendly, so you'll love every moment spent making these pixel masterpieces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/fd5d7b9b6a079581f96c8f8883d45393.poster.avif?t=1729573730\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/fd5d7b9b6a079581f96c8f8883d45393.webm?t=1729573730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244050/extras/fd5d7b9b6a079581f96c8f8883d45393.mp4?t=1729573730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paint by Pixel is the perfect game for when you want something cute, cozy, and fun to do. It's great for your creative moments and super easy to pick up and play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try and see how much fun you can have creating pixel art!</p>",
